						<summary>

						<p>This epigraph which is damaged seems to record the gift of some jewels by Tāṉañjaṉ Nārāyaṇaṉ of Puḷḷamaṅgalam in Kalār-kūṟṟam.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in the reign of Parāntaka I. The date may be any year from thirty-one to thirty-nine.</p>						

						</summary>
